ShadowGolem.DisplayName: Shadow Golem
ShadowGuard.DisplayName: Shadow Guard

CrystalFairy: {
	DisplayName: Crystal Fairy
	BestiaryDescription: Small fairies from magic crystal caves! They love eating magic crystals. When they find magic crystals in the wild, they try to bring them back to the caves. People have made magic bait based on this habit to find crystal caves.
}

CrystalSpirit: {
	DisplayName: Crystal Spirit
	BestiaryDescription: Their heads are smooth magic crystals that emit magike waves to detect nearby enemies.
}

CrystalGolem: {
	DisplayName: Crystal Golem
	BestiaryDescription: Large magic crystals are very rare, and crystal golems made from them are even rarer! Every step of a Crystal Golem causes a minor earthquake. It can also gather magike into its head and fire a laser to attack enemies.
}

CrystalEye: {
	DisplayName: Crystal Eye
	BestiaryDescription: A fully crystallized Demon Eye. The strong daylight damages its fragile lens crystalline structure, so it only appears at night.
}

