	Name0: Crysilly
	Name1: CRS: c000
	Name2: Crysta
	Name3: Mogik
	StandardDialogue1: You look a bit low on magike!
	StandardDialogue2: Need to replenish magike to maintain bodily functions.
	StandardDialogue3: Magic crystal, delicious.
	StandardDialogue4: In the sky, there are past companions.
	StandardDialogue5: Magic crystal cave, comfortable.
	CommonDialogue1: I need a large amount of magic crystals. I will trade useful materials with you.
	RareDialogue1: Fairies and sprites, powerful and full of wisdom.
	RareDialogue2: Coral... ... data not unlocked.
	RareDialogue3: The ancient dragons have traveled through time to be here.
	BestiaryDescription: A small robot powered by magike that needs to regularly consume magic crystals. Bring it magic crystals and it will gladly craft various magike tools for you.
}

