	Name7: Felix
	Chat1: Observing these little ones is very entertaining, I often spend an entire day watching them.
	Chat2: Fairies have their favorite walls, you can see them in front of these walls.
	Chat3: Do you know about magike dust? Fairies love this kind of powdered magic.
	Chat4: If you want to catch fairies, make a vine snare!
	Chat5: Capturing and raising fairies is quite common, but don't overdo it!
	Chat6: Have you seen Coral? She brought me here.
	Chat7: Perhaps one day you will encounter the space fairy and complete its trial.
	DryadChat1: Is that the Dryad? I haven't seen her in a long time.
	DryadChat2: The Dryad once fought against Cthulhu here, and I was in another world... such memorable times.
	DryadChat3: The scent of the forest emanates from the Dryad, I love that smell.
}

