EyeOfGlistent.DisplayName: Eye Of Glistent
ServantOfGlistent.DisplayName: Servant Of Glistent

CrystallineHumming: {
	DisplayName: Crystalline Humming
	BestiaryDescription: A bird-like creature made of crystalline magike crystals. It is speculated that they may share a common ancestor with the Moss Hornets of the jungle.
}

CrystallineVinicColumn: {
	DisplayName: Crystalline Vinic Column
	BestiaryDescription: A creature formed when an abandoned crystal pillar is parasitized by crystalline duckweed. It usually remains motionless, disguised as a crystal pillar. Once approached, it suddenly attacks, and its sharp crystals can easily pierce armor.
}

CrystallineVinicLaser: {
	DisplayName: Crystalline Vinic Laser
	BestiaryDescription: A creature formed when an abandoned laser is parasitized by crystalline duckweed. It usually remains motionless, disguised as a laser. Once approached, it suddenly attacks, and the laser core grants it the ability to fire beams.
}

CrystallineSentinel.DisplayName: Crystalline Sentinel

WildMabird: {
	DisplayName: Wild Mabird
	BestiaryDescription: Originally man-made machines, but over the long years and the influence of magike, they became living creatures. They perform dive attacks on their targets.
}

WildMabirdNest: {
	DisplayName: Wild Mabird Nest
	BestiaryDescription: Nests built by wild mabirds that continuously hatch new wild mabirds. When a target is detected, they launch the mabirds inside.
}

